    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game where you can keep a Chiyari-style lizard on your PC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can pet it or grab it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lizards have feelings and show you their actions according to their feelings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can manage your lizard by turning them on/off and changing their names on the menu screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a total of 8 different lizard chicks in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's create a healing space by increasing the number of your lizard to your heart's content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras/a5338f1771c570a8c06f60b3703d04a3.poster.avif?t=1729436638\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras/a5338f1771c570a8c06f60b3703d04a3.webm?t=1729436638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How To Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras/41b77ddb1c6f0d74f87b9e57de497eae.avif?t=1729436638\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras_big/41b77ddb1c6f0d74f87b9e57de497eae.avif?t=1729436638 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Lizard】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can be stroked or grabbed by mouse operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behavior changes with emotion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They will lay eggs when they grow up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please love them a lot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras/ac0a4559c0b0101e7b27b18cb29e1f88.avif?t=1729436638\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras_big/ac0a4559c0b0101e7b27b18cb29e1f88.avif?t=1729436638 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Menu】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can grab it and move it around by mouse operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The menu opens when you release it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras/646f5e044e7a0cb93bb3594ef1314347.avif?t=1729436638\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras_big/646f5e044e7a0cb93bb3594ef1314347.avif?t=1729436638 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Food】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can grab it and move it around by mouse operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the contents run out, you can replenish them by clicking on them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras/8fc0d288998a05405532f1524753c3ab.avif?t=1729436638\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162170/extras_big/8fc0d288998a05405532f1524753c3ab.avif?t=1729436638 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Garbage can】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can grab it and move it around by mouse operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can dump feces and eggs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a derivative work of “Touhou Project”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It has nothing to do with Shanghai Alice Gengakudan.</p>",
